diet_importance.Description: subject's self-rating of how important dieting is to them

appetite_pre.Description: subject's self-rating of appetite strength when asked before the scan

appetite_post.Description: subject's self-rating of appetite strength when asked after the scan

oral_contraceptive.Description: whether or not the subject was using an oral contraceptive

days_since_menstruation.LongName: Days Since Last Menstruation (Day in Cycle)
days_since_menstruation.Description: number of days since last menstruation

cycle_phase_covariate.Description: Menstrual Cycle phase (based on days_since_menstruation and oral_contraceptive
cycle_phase_covariate.Units: 0 = Not in phase 1 or 2 (29 days or more) or using oral contraceptives, 1 = Follicular phase/ovulation (day 1-14), 2 = Luteal phase (day 15 to 28)
